*NEW* Apple Cider, Maple & Toasted Pecans cookie recipe is live on the site! 

This cookie so soft and packed with a ton of fall flavors. The sugar coating gives the cookie a gorgeous snowy look and also helps bring out the flavors. Click the link in my bio to bake yours today! 

#TheDessertPantry

*NEW* Apple Cider, Maple & Toasted Pecans - rollout version. Featuring a special appearance by @buttermilkbysam Apple Cider Caramel. 

This recipe is delicious, full of flavor, and if you decide to top of apple cider caramel, Royal icing or buttercream, I can promise you won’t be disappointed by any of your choices. Or keep it simple and eat as is. 

The recipe is live on the site. Click the link in my bio to make yours today. And if you do make it, please don’t forget to leave a star rating and comment on what you thought of it!! 

#TheDessertPantry

This week I’ll be diving into decorating sugar cookies with both royal icing and buttercream. It’s been a minute since I’ve done either so this should be fun. 

So here is a throwback to some holiday cookies I made last year. 🎄❄️☃️ Are you guys also up to your elbows in flour? 😆

#TheDessertPantry

❄️ Holiday cookie box 2022 ❄️ This holiday season I didn’t get to create or share as much as I had planned, but still happy to have been able to do create. Happy holidays from my family to yours ❤️

All cookies in this box are my own recipe with the exception of the apple cider caramel which is from @buttermilkbysam. Recipes available on the website. 

#TheDessertPantry

Hi! I’m back after a month break, and happy to share a few recipe updates! This Strawberry Sugar Cookie got an update to be a NO CHILL 🥳 it comes together in under an hour (prep + bake), and is soft and full of flavor. 

This gorgeous color block was inspired by @loveandoliveoil 

Click the link in my bio and find it under the ‘Cookie Recipe’ tab. #TheDessertPantry

Blueberry Lemon Sugar Cookies got an upgrade to NO CHILL 🥳 A few recipe tweaks really helped elevate the flavor of this cookie, and it all comes together from prep to bake in under an hour. 

Click the link in my bio and search ‘Blueberry Lemon Sugar Cookies’ to make yours today 😄 #TheDessertPantry

#sugarcookies #cookies #galletas #cookierecipe #recipes #cookievideo #lemoncookies #blueberrycookies #dessert #baking #dessertrecipe

Next leveled up recipe - my Vanilla sugar cookie. This one is also now a no chill recipe, but still soft and delicious. Reusing the photo from last year when I decorated with @thejungalow inspired colors. 

Click the link in my bio and search ‘Vanilla Sugar Cookie’ to make yours today. #TheDessertPantry

Taste the Rainbow 🌈 Spring usually means I start mixing up a TON of colors. This time around I used just the 3 primary colors - red, yellow and blue - to create alllll these colors. *sigh* Color mixing is probably one of my favorite things to do. 

Color theory is a topic I’ll be adding to the list for Subscribers. I reset on my action plan for Subscriptions and will be slowly adding in content exclusive to those who sign up. I won’t be ready until probably March but I’ll make sure to let everyone know when I have the content up.  #TheDessertPantry

First cake of 2023! Two new things with this one - 1) recipe is from Sam @buttermilkbysam and it’s her butter cake recipe (omg so good). 2) I am finallyyy practicing palette knife painting (talk about a challenge!). Sheet cakes are going to be my thing in 2023 - so much easier to decorate in my opinion 😁

Design inspired by @amylockwoodart beautiful artwork. All the colors used were from @colour.mill  and I used only the 3 primary colors. I’ll be sharing more details to Subscribers in March. 

So, tell me, what do you think? Have you tried palette knife painting and how did you like it? #TheDessertPantry

Also excited to share a new Let’s Create section that is dedicated entirely to helping you learn how to decorate and create your own show-stopping desserts at home. 

There is a lot more coming down the pipe and email subscribers are already getting details about what is on the horizon. Sign up today via the link in bio if you want to be in the know.
